statements: SELECT * FROM PharmacyData WHERE medication_name = 'Aspirin';

SELECT medication_name, prescription_date FROM PharmacyData WHERE patient_id = 1001;
SELECT * FROM PharmacyData WHERE dosage LIKE '%mg%';
SELECT prescription_date, medication_name FROM PharmacyData WHERE patient_id = 2002;
SELECT * FROM PharmacyData WHERE patient_id = 1001
SELECT medication_name, dosage FROM PharmacyData WHERE patient_id = 1002 ORDER BY prescription_date DESC
SELECT * FROM PharmacyData WHERE medication_name LIKE 'Aspirin%'
SELECT patient_id, medication_name, dosage FROM PharmacyData WHERE prescription_date BETWEEN '2022-06-01' AND '2022-06-30'
SELECT COUNT(patient_id) AS total_patients, AVG(patient_id) AS avg_patient_id FROM PharmacyData
SELECT * FROM pharmacy_customers;
SELECT customer_name, address FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE customer_id = 1;
SELECT customer_name, address, phone_number FROM pharmacy_customers ORDER BY customer_name DESC;
SELECT medication_name, dosage, date_prescribed FROM medication_records WHERE customer_id = 2 ORDER BY date_prescribed ASC;
SELECT customer_name, medication_name, dosage FROM pharmacy_customers JOIN medication_records ON pharmacy_customers.customer_id = medication_records.customer_id WHERE customer_name LIKE 'A%'
SELECT * FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE customer_id = 1;
SELECT customer_name, address FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE customer_id > 5 ORDER BY address ASC;
SELECT medication_name, dosage, date_prescribed FROM medication_records WHERE dosage >= 50 ORDER BY date_prescribed DESC;
SELECT customer_name, phone_number FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE address LIKE '%Ave%' OR address LIKE '%Street%';

SELECT p.customer_name, m.medication_name, m.dosage, m.date_prescribed FROM pharmacy_customers p JOIN medication_records m ON p.customer_id = m.customer_id WHERE m.date_prescribed BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT * FROM pharmacy_customers;
SELECT customer_name, age FROM pharmacy_customers ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT customer_name, address FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE age > 30;
SELECT * FROM medication_inventory WHERE price < 50.00;
SELECT prescription_id, customer_name, medication_name, doctor_name, prescription_date FROM prescription_history;
SELECT * FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY customer_name ASC;
SELECT medication_name, quantity, price FROM medication_inventory WHERE quantity < 50 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT customer_id, customer_name, age, address FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE customer_name LIKE 'J%' ORDER BY age;
SELECT customer_name, medication_name, doctor_name, prescription_date FROM pharmacy_customers JOIN prescription_history ON pharmacy_customers.customer_id = prescription_history.customer_id;
SELECT DISTINCT customer_name, age FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE age >= 18 AND age <= 60 ORDER BY age ASC, customer_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM Pharmacy;
SELECT medication_name, dosage_form FROM Medication;
SELECT insurance_provider, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date FROM HealthInsurance WHERE insurance_id = 1;
SELECT patient_id, medication_id, prescription_date, dosage, insurance_id FROM PharmacyAnalytics WHERE claim_status = 'approved';
SELECT patient_id, medication_name, dosage, insurance_provider FROM Pharmacy JOIN Medication ON Pharmacy.medication_id = Medication.medication_id;
SELECT * FROM Pharmacy;
SELECT medication_name, manufacturer, dosage_form FROM Medication WHERE medication_id = 5;
SELECT patient_id, medication_name, prescription_date FROM PharmacyAnalytics WHERE claim_status = 'approved' ORDER BY prescription_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM HealthInsurance WHERE insurance_provider LIKE '%Aetna%';
SELECT patient_id, medication_name, insurance_provider, claim_status FROM PharmacyAnalytics JOIN HealthInsurance ON PharmacyAnalytics.insurance_id = HealthInsurance.insurance_id;
SELECT * FROM pharmacy_customers;
SELECT customer_name, customer_age FROM pharmacy_customers ORDER BY customer_age DESC;
SELECT medication_name, medication_price FROM medications WHERE medication_price > 50;
SELECT * FROM prescriptions WHERE prescription_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY prescription_date ASC;
SELECT customer_name, medication_name, usage_quantity FROM pharmacy_customers JOIN medication_usage ON pharmacy_customers.customer_id = medication_usage.customer_id;
SELECT * FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE customer_age > 50;
SELECT customer_name, customer_gender FROM pharmacy_customers WHERE customer_gender = 'Male';
SELECT medication_name, medication_price FROM medications WHERE medication_category = 'Pain Relief' ORDER BY medication_price DESC;

SELECT pc.customer_name, pm.medication_name, p.prescription_date FROM pharmacy_customers pc INNER JOIN prescriptions p ON pc.customer_id = p.customer_id INNER JOIN medications pm ON p.medication_id = pm.medication_id WHERE pc.customer_age < 30 ORDER BY p.prescription_date DESC;

SELECT pc.customer_name, mi.plan_name, mi.plan_type FROM pharmacy_customers pc LEFT JOIN medication_usage mu ON pc.customer_id = mu.customer_id LEFT JOIN insurance_plans mi ON pc.customer_id = mi.plan_id WHERE mu.usage_quantity > 5 AND mi.plan_coverage > 50;
